Job Title: IT Manager - Mid level 

Location: Riyadh

Job Description:
As the IT Manager, you will oversee the information technology department and manage the implementation of new technologies. You will ensure the security and efficiency of our IT infrastructure while providing strategic direction for the organization’s technology needs.

Key Responsibilities:
- Develop and implement IT strategies aligned with business goals.
- Oversee the maintenance of IT systems and infrastructure.
- Ensure data security and compliance with relevant regulations.
- Coordinate with other departments to support their technology needs.
- Manage IT budgets and optimize costs.

Qualifications:
- Bachelor’s degree in Information Technology, Computer Science, or a related field.
- Proven experience as an IT Manager or similar role.
- Strong knowledge of IT systems, networks, and security.
- Excellent leadership and project management skills.
- Effective communication and interpersonal abilities.

How to Apply:

Interested candidates are invited to send their resume to jobs@altanmiyah.edu.sa with the subject line "IT Manager Application".